    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sound BMW E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L straight-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This example delivers exceptional visceral feedback through its Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. Essential preventative maintenance has been performed, including a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity under high lateral loads. The chassis is dialed in with Bilstein dampers and refreshed bushings, maintaining the precision of its MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension. While the aesthetics show honest patina consistent with its age, the drivetrain remains robust and the power delivery is linear and aggressive. A true driver\u2019s spec for the purist seeking analog performance.",
      "price": 31500.0,
