      "description": "This meticulously maintained sedan offers the perfect balance of performance and practicality. The exterior shines in a deep metallic charcoal, showing only minor road chips on the front bumper consistent with careful highway driving. Inside, the premium leather upholstery remains supple and free of tears, with only light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. All cabin electronics, including the high-definition infotainment system and dual-zone climate control, function flawlessly. Mechanically, the vehicle is in great shape; it has received regular synthetic oil changes every 5,000 miles, and the brake pads and rotors were recently serviced. The tires are matching all-seasons with plenty of tread depth remaining on the factory 18-inch alloy wheels. This car has been smoke-free and garage-kept, providing a smooth, quiet ride that feels tight and responsive. It comes with a complete service history and both original key fobs.",
